title: Núñez Stars As Haaland Flops
description:
The FC crew break down Liverpool's 3-1 victory over Manchester City and compare the performances of new strikers Darwin Núñez and Erling Haaland after contrasting performances from the young stars. Plus, Archie Rhind-Tutt and Arne Friedrich join the show to react to Bayern Munich's dominant Supercup display.
